location.fullValue: Pearl Plan, Brooks at Riverview Landing

data.description: Just the perfect location in close-in Cobb County. Traditional townhome with fireside Great Room which gets lots of natural daylight, separate formal Dining Room leading out to the rear patio/fenced in back yard great for outdoor entertaining. The Eat-in Kitchen features a pass through into the Dining Room along with stainless steel appliance package with refrigerator, gas range, microwave range hood and dishwasher. The second level is where all of the bedrooms are. The primary Bedroom is spacious with a nice primary Bathroom with dual vanities, garden tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. The additional two bedrooms are also nice with a hall bathroom for guests. The Laundry Room is on the second level with Laundry Room, washer and dryer will remain with the property at no additional cost to the buyer.
